{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.640", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die erste Tafel wurde 1993 gegr\u00fcndet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.000", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Inzwischen gibt es 934\u00a0Tafeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.080", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass es die Tafeln gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.920", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist das Verdienst vieler Ehrenamtlicher. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.040", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass es die Tafeln in diesem Land braucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.760", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist das Versagen aller bisherigen Bundesregierungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.240", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.560", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch diese Bundesregierung aus Union und SPD betreibt beim Kampf gegen Armut Arbeitsverweigerung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.040", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage es einmal so: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.520", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ein Hartz\u2011IV-Betroffener bei der Suche nach Arbeit so wenig Einsatz zeigen w\u00fcrde wie diese Regierung beim Kampf gegen Armut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er w\u00e4re schon l\u00e4ngst mit einigen Sanktionen belegt und sein Arbeitslosengeld\u00a0II w\u00e4re wahrscheinlich um mindestens 60\u00a0Prozent gek\u00fcrzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn nicht gar gestrichen worden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.560", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Halten wir fest: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.440", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "16\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also 13\u00a0Millionen Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.120", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind hierzulande von Armut bedroht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.160", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Politik reagiert auf diesen Missstand sehr unterschiedlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.320", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt einzelne Minister wie Jens Spahn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.240", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Arme belehren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man mit dem Geld doch gut \u00fcber die Runden kommt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.400", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als ob er eine Ahnung davon h\u00e4tte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.560", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie man mit 416\u00a0Euro im Monat \u00fcber die Runden kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.840", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wehe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Waschmaschine geht kaputt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.360", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Neoliberalen spielen Arme ohne Arbeit und Arme mit Arbeit gegeneinander aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.800", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als ob ein Niedriglohnbetroffener auch nur einen Cent mehr in der Tasche h\u00e4tte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.720", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn der Hartz\u2011IV-Regelsatz gezielt kleingerechnet wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Gegenteil ist doch der Fall."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.960", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die ganz Rechten reden den Armen ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man m\u00fcsse nur alle Ausl\u00e4nder abschieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.240", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann w\u00fcrde wieder Wohlstand f\u00fcr alle herrschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.760", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als ob die arme Rentnerin nur einen Cent mehr in der Tasche h\u00e4tte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.600", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Gefl\u00fcchtete in Kriegsgebiete abgeschoben werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.880", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tatsache ist doch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.520", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir hatten schon viel zu niedrige Renten und viel zu niedrige L\u00f6hne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.560", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bevor die Gefl\u00fcchteten gekommen sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linke sagen hingegen klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.800", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Gesellschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.680", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der alle Menschen garantiert vor Armut gesch\u00fctzt sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.640", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist machbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.240", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieses Parlament m\u00fcsste nur die richtigen sozialen Alternativen umsetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.000", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit meine ich nicht die Ma\u00dfnahmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Ihnen Ihre Freunde von Goldman Sachs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also die Lobby der Finanzspekulation, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einreden m\u00f6chten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.560", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sicherheit vor Kinderarmut ist m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.600", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel durch eine Kindergrundsicherung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.080", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die alle Kinder garantiert vor Armut sch\u00fctzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit einem breiten B\u00fcndnis streiten wir daf\u00fcr; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn jedes Kind hat das Recht auf einen guten Start ins Leben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sicherheit vor Armut ist m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.760", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir das Hartz\u2011IV-Sanktionssystem abschaffen und durch gute Arbeit und eine sanktionsfreie Mindestsicherung in H\u00f6he von 1\u00a0050\u00a0Euro ersetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.400", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sicherheit vor Altersarmut ist m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.560", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir das Rentenniveau erh\u00f6hen und eine solidarische Mindestrente in H\u00f6he von 1\u00a0050\u00a0Euro als unteres Sicherheitsnetz einf\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Sicherheit vor Armut ist finanzierbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.160", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssten nur den Mumm haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.160", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Millionenerbschaften und Gewinne aus Finanzspekulationen st\u00e4rker zu besteuern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Frage ist doch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.600", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Will man weiter Million\u00e4rserben besch\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder will man endlich Millionen in diesem Lande vor Armut sch\u00fctzen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linke haben uns entschieden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen der Armut den Kampf an."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.120", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.760", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.560", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Katja Kipping.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.520", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stephan Stracke f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
